column5: As I was looking at the pictures I thought that they were legit all from the game. That’s how good this is, nice job.
My mom is the same way
It doesn’t necessarily mean that they are albert fans if they are on color. The myth still has potential. But I get what you mean.
Yeah, I get what you mean. But it can still be a good game with or without robux. The character can still have a good story and stuff.
Just because someone can’t spend robux on anything for their game doesn’t mean they can’t be a myth.
Yeah, to be honest I don’t like the neck either.
I’m trying to learn how to draw more realistically. Sorry I drew Waylon in this style.
It’s just my style of drawing.
